Main components of Porject are: 
Sectoral mainstreaming including knowledge management for coastal and marine biodiversity conservation. 
Institutional Capacity Development. 
Sustainable Community Livelihoods and Natural Resource Use in the Godavari River Estuary.

project_descr: Mainstreaming Coastal and Marine Biodiversity Conservation into Production Sectors in the East Godavari Estuary, Andhra Pradesh
